# SOURCE: Official IQFeed FAQ lists login.interquote.com and the 66.112.149.138-150 / 66.112.149.202-225 ranges on ports 60000-60050.

DOMAIN,login.interquote.com
DOMAIN,iqhelp.dtn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,iqfeed.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,interquote.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dtn.com

